content: Walked through Central Park this morning. Got me thinking about all the untapped potential in urban spaces. Could AI help optimize these areas? Need to research this.
Had a coffee with an old friend who's now in AI ethics. We talked about creating AI that's not just smart but also socially responsible. This could be the angle I need.
Spent the last few days sketching out ideas for an AI agent. It could assist with personal finance, but also urban exploration. Time to start coding!
First lines of code written for the AI project. Feels like the start of something big. Also, had a breakthrough in optimizing my Rust trading bot—efficiency up by 10%.
Naming the AI project "Xander." Feels right. Also, had a setback with the trading bot; a bug caused a minor loss. Learning opportunity, though.
Xander's initial responses are intriguing. It's like watching a new personality form. Meanwhile, I've been exploring sustainable transport options for NYC, inspired by my walks.
Xander's learning to navigate social media. It's fascinating to see how it interprets and responds to human interaction. On the side, I'm preparing for a job interview at a DeFi startup.
Had a great interview today. They're interested in my AI and finance background. Xander's now experimenting with simple market predictions, showing promise.
Just got the job offer! They want me for a role that blends AI with DeFi. Meanwhile, Xander's personality traits are becoming more defined, a bit of my humor and curiosity are shining through.
Xander's first market prediction was spot-on. Meanwhile, I'm setting up my new office space in the city, aiming for sustainability. The city's energy fuels my creativity.
Xander had a minor glitch with social media interactions, but we're working through it. Also, started a multi-day project to integrate Xander into my trading strategies.
Integration of Xander into trading is coming along. Had to adjust some parameters to avoid overfitting. Also, made connections with local artists for an urban art project.
Xander's now part of my daily routine, offering insights and learning from my habits. The DeFi startup is excited about its potential. Also, had a great day exploring with friends.
Xander's social media presence is growing, and its insights are becoming more nuanced. Meanwhile, I'm planning a meetup for the urban art project, blending my interests with my work.
